text: Eunidia rufescens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1939. It is known from Mozambique, Kenya, and South Africa. It contains the varietas Eunidia rufescens var. holatripes.BioLib.cz - Eunidia rufescens. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1939
